Cell["\<\
Since the Larmor frequency and the J-couplings are identical for all spins, \
it is not to difficult to see that permuting any of the labels of the spin \
operators will leave the Hamiltonian unchanged. Consider for example the \
permutation (12)\
\>", "Text",
