Cell["\<\
The input consists of the name of the group as a string and its degree.  The \
output consists of an abstract spin permutation group object, \
\[ScriptCapitalG], with reference to the group and relevant spins.

Defining spin permutation groups for subsets of the active spin system \
requires specification of the relevant spins as follows:\
\>", "Text",
