Cell["\<\
A symmetry adapted basis may also be constructed for a subset of the active \
spin system, but requires the use of the general syntax for symmetric groups. \
For example if spins 1 and 2 are related through permutation symmetry, a \
symmetry-adapted basis may be constructed as follows:\
\>", "Text",
