Cell["\<\
Construction of a symmetry-adapted basis with respect to an arbitrary group \
requires specification of the group elements. 

Consider for example the Dihedral group of degree 3, which represents the \
symmetry group of an equilateral triangle. The group elements are given by:\
\>", "Text",
