Cell[TextData[{
 "Consider a generic Hamiltonian H given by:\n\n",
 StyleBox["H ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["=", TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"8a01baa6-60d2-4c6f-b4a7-7fda27374030"],
 " ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubsuperscriptBox["\[CapitalSigma]", "j", "N"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"0aab0546-302d-4eff-9784-c78e4421a17f"],
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["x", "j"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"86b7ba30-e3c6-45c2-a09d-ac8da47867ba"],
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["X", "j"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"fbf58c26-fa03-4d2a-8000-55d2a99d95b9"],
 "\n\nThe time-evolution operator for short times may be written as\n\n",
 StyleBox["U(\[Delta]t) \[TildeEqual] 1- i\[Delta]t H\n\n",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "Suppose we are interested in density operator components that are \
time-invariant.",
 StyleBox["\n\n",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"b1c8e26a-6879-4ec0-b823-bbd3481458a5"],
 StyleBox["(t)=U(t)",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"71326733-2e1c-431b-9625-989ec457004c"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["U", "\[Dagger]"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"cb7061df-4119-442f-995d-21ac172809c0"],
 StyleBox["(t)=",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"02bbb122-fe8c-4a4a-8a86-d402b3e8c5d8"],
 StyleBox["\n\n",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "In particular this has to hold for small time steps:",
 StyleBox["\n\n",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"259d1675-6a89-47df-be61-908f61dfad8b"],
 StyleBox["(\[Delta]t) = U(\[Delta]t)",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"55f222c7-dc21-4847-9090-26b34286a969"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["U", "\[Dagger]"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"5982c7df-7a4a-4cb5-aeac-0ca6f291d0e5"],
 StyleBox["(\[Delta]t) \[TildeEqual] ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"6f24c697-1b3b-4351-a998-2903b117be10"],
 StyleBox[" -i \[Delta]t [H,",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"f903a49b-0c8d-477b-b3b7-3265152eeb5f"],
 StyleBox["]\n\n",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "Time-invariance of a particular spin density operator component is thus \
guaranteed by confirming that",
 StyleBox["\n\n[H,",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"90d30eda-4772-4181-a9b8-7e2f501f80d6"],
 StyleBox["]= 0 \[Implies] [",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["X", "j"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"90b2ba71-87de-4628-87bf-1c3c789a7ad1"],
 StyleBox[", ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"961f048e-13a1-4988-a42d-b7a47c3a8481"],
 StyleBox["] = 0 \[ForAll] j\n",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "\nsince the generators are in general linearly-independent.\n\nThe routine ",
 StyleBox["Commutant ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "goes one step further and",
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "answers the reverse question: given a set of generators ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    SubscriptBox["X", "1"]}], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"e57fc4a2-4468-4d09-b024-533ab7b21576"],
 StyleBox[", ..., ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["X", "N"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"fd4d6091-044c-4c11-8616-f9239e0aa1b2"],
 StyleBox["}",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ",",
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "what are the spin density operator components ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"e6274649-4214-49a2-b969-6fe4c578b5ea"],
 " that are time-invariant under an arbitrary Hamiltonian ",
 StyleBox["H = ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubsuperscriptBox["\[CapitalSigma]", "j", "N"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"fc0821be-7a6f-4b37-8497-db4bc707c477"],
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["x", "j"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"be90ee14-c8b2-4a57-bef2-c7ac4c9cd47a"],
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["X", "j"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"8f24b1b2-a6e6-42ea-b60f-db209a71b8a6"],
 " ?"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.728220896380918*^9, 3.728221063488654*^9}, {
