Cell[TextData[{
 "The result above indicates that starting from thermal ",
 StyleBox["z",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "-magnetisation it would be impossible to conduct any useful NMR \
experiments. Of course, this is not too surprising, since we haven\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]t added in the possibility of applying any pulses. The \
pulse algebra is given by: "
}], "Text",
