Cell[TextData[{
 "A permutation symmetric spin-relaxation process will in general lead to a \
permutation symmetric relaxation superoperator. The relaxation superoperator \
( ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   OverscriptBox["\[CapitalGamma]", "^"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "9739cb17-fdbe-4ab1-8af1-4c70d4db5f86"],
 " ) may then be represented as a linear combination of double-commutation \
superoperators originating from the set {",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["Q", "*"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "530552d8-340f-4320-a35e-f4573ee4e101"],
 "}:\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   OverscriptBox["\[CapitalGamma]", "^"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"d30e2bdc-0e42-4f25-9ce4-e6efd72d77cd"],
 StyleBox[" = - ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[CapitalSigma]", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"395a34b7-f083-46ac-a384-81e66ebacad3"],
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["\[Gamma]", "k"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"6f7919fc-5823-43f2-bfb9-eff58abb955d"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox[
    RowBox[{
     OverscriptBox[
      RowBox[{"(", 
       SubsuperscriptBox["Q", "k", "*"]}], "^"], ")"}], "\[Dagger]"], 
   TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"f10ab8a6-1aa6-420e-8677-e090ba212afc"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   OverscriptBox[
    SubsuperscriptBox["Q", "k", "*"], "^"], TraditionalForm]],
  FontWeight->"Bold",ExpressionUUID->"130a2dd2-848a-4ebb-b0ee-cfc679306bfc"],
 "\n\nSince the relaxation superoperator acts through commutation, the \
condition for an operator ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "LLS"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "b6d08450-6739-4d66-bcc1-dd9f0b5bad96"],
 " to be long-lived is equivalent to demanding that the operator ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "LLS"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "4ac1f648-ec6f-49ca-971d-413d824a6a7e"],
 " commutes with all operator in the set {",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["Q", "*"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0634da8d-b96b-4975-af53-bf697945f8e8"],
 "}. In other words an operator is long-lived if and only if it is an element \
of the commutant of {",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["Q", "*"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e44e5f66-72b8-4be2-a0cb-21a99b4f9de9"],
 "}. But since the operators {",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["Q", "*"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "67de84a4-a631-4797-8d47-ec3e857632da"],
 "} are themselves elements of the commutant of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["S", "3"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "256c8716-2727-4959-bce2-7c96adf51ea8"],
 " we may deduce:\n\n",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "LLS"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "df73c2b5-e579-4536-ac7b-8035bfc78930"],
 " \[DoubleLeftRightArrow] ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "LLS"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "0afb6564-daa4-4106-8014-dd07f71b9274"],
 " \[Element] C({",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["Q", "*"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "37594ab7-627c-4e1c-9f55-6af5f2b4e9b3"],
 "}) \[DoubleLeftRightArrow] ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["Q", "LLS"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "efd6c36f-f85f-4d78-af95-3144a0b4677a"],
 " \[Element] C(C({",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["S", "3"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "31fe4255-5afd-4a49-ac75-c278ca99c16f"],
 "})) = ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["C", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "323ecb66-7132-4023-8be3-180f1627d5da"],
 "({",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["S", "3"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c79b5bed-309e-4b36-9894-6316e2f8b597"],
 "}) \n\nWe may verify this fact explicitly by first calculating the \
commutant of  {",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["Q", "*"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "f0b6b559-9124-4f43-8871-fda1b80fe0d7"],
 "}"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.728220896380918*^9, 3.728221063488654*^9}, {
