   3.852923110173602*^9}, {3.852971394261127*^9, 3.852971409646491*^9}, {
   3.852971648338273*^9, 3.8529716488850155`*^9}, {3.852971830588436*^9, 
   3.852971832103771*^9}},
 Background->RGBColor[
  1, 0.925, 0.925],ExpressionUUID->"20733ea9-8277-4385-9428-750c29a5bc89"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Consider the case of three identical spins with total angular momentum ",
 StyleBox["I",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ". The symmetry group of such a system is ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["S", "3"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "7ade06a0-8e4d-47fe-b4cb-adf1de753bde"],
 ", which is isomorphic to ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["C", 
    RowBox[{"3", "v"}]], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "55cc4124-f3b0-4a56-8b13-99797c13e5a8"],
 ". The group ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["C", 
    RowBox[{"3", "v"}]], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6dec162b-5ae4-44b1-a3e8-bacd0e2f7afe"],
 " is known to possess three irreducible representations: ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    SubscriptBox["A", "1"]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "c871a1fd-bd08-439e-be1c-b2f5ab764eb1"],
 ",",
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubscriptBox["A", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "091e39fe-8832-4ac2-8174-8161de6d3c54"],
 ",  ",
 StyleBox["E",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "}. How do these irreducible representations pair up for three identical \
spin-1/2 particles? The dual pairings for an identical three-spin-1/2 system \
are given by:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.728220896380918*^9, 3.728221063488654*^9}, {
   3.7282211222267337`*^9, 3.728221130577482*^9}, {3.7282211686435347`*^9, 
   3.728221248183666*^9}, {3.728221349247451*^9, 3.7282214691937075`*^9}, {
   3.728221527829361*^9, 3.728221552814209*^9}, {3.7282216003270726`*^9, 
   3.728221618069004*^9}, {3.728221749143102*^9, 3.728221782481998*^9}, {
   3.728221829178913*^9, 3.728221832894768*^9}, {3.728221963693866*^9, 
   3.728222069737784*^9}, {3.728222247511516*^9, 3.728222251930869*^9}, {
